title: The Beet Organic Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, Organic, Beer/Wine, Canadian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Organic cafe with a menu designed by a certified nutritionist and a homeopathic doctor. Vegan and wheat-free labeled. Menu is around 70%+ vegetarian/vegan. Offers weekend brunch. Sustainable interior design. Uses biodegradable packaging. Supports local farmers.
